name: Outflank
Lore: 'Commander Igar''s defense of Endor called for the use of speeder bikes to harass any attacking Rebels.',
Text: 'During a battle, if you have weapons at both sites adjacent to that battle, add 3 to your total power and add one battle destiny. OR For remainder of turn, your biker scout at an exterior site is power +1 and adds 1 to each of that character''s weapon destiny draws.',
